pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultiboost Lecithin 1200mg 150 Caps
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost Lecithin is a premium quality formula to support healthy liver function and assist fat metabolism.

Liver Health: Lecithin contains choline, which supports healthy liver function and helps maintain liver health.

Fat Metabolism: The choline in lecithin assists fat metabolism.

Source of Phospholipids: Lecithin is a source of phospholipids, an important component of cell membranes.

General Wellbeing: Choline in lecithin helps maintain general health and wellbeing.

Derived from Soybeans: Naturally sourced from soybeans.

Size: 150 Capsules

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS: LECITHIN.

LECITHIN 1.2 g

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE: Five capsules daily or as directed by a healthcare professional. The recommended daily dose of this medicine contains 50 mg of potassium.

Five capsules daily, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
